HEADWORD: Basyle
<hw>Bas"yle</hw> <pr>(b⟦acr⟧s"⟦icr⟧l <it>or</it> b⟦amac⟧s"⟦icr⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>ba`sis</grk> base + <grk>"y`lh</grk> wood.
